# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Chill with Kiritan — root .gitignore
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dependencies & build output
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/build/

# Rust / Tauri build artifacts
**/target/

# Vite / tooling caches
**/.vite/
*.local

# Logs & debug
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp

# Probe / headless-test scratch (regenerated on demand)
**/.probe_tmp/

# ── License-restricted assets — NEVER commit or push ──────────
# Redistribution-PROHIBITED model: ふらすこ式風東北きりたん (kiritan.vrm).
# VRMA motion pack: the pack's terms forbid redistributing the .vrma files.
# (Global patterns = belt-and-suspenders across every location.)
*.vrm
*.vrma

# Raw glTF JSON extracted FROM kiritan.vrm (derived model data)
tools/output/

# Local-only retention bin — holds the VRMA pack .zip, model renders, installers
_archive/

# Font with unconfirmed redistribution license.
# If verified OFL (WDXL Lubrifont), re-add with:  git add -f path/to/the.otf
WD-XLLubrifontJPN-Regular.otf

# Secrets / credentials
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.keystore
